snippet.title: "Alice: Asylum" Patreon Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Join American McGee and the Alice community as we return to fractured-but-familiar Wonderland, with old friends twisted by guilt and rage. Get early access to creative output and a direct line of communication with American and the community at http://www.patreon.com/americanmcgee ! We hope you will join us and The Insane Children in The Asylum and get your voice heard in the creation of the world's first ever crowd-designed triple-A game.
